HEADWORD: Impuberal
<hw>Im*pu"ber*al</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧m*p⟦umac⟧"b⟦etil⟧r*⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <def>Not having arrived at puberty; immature.</def>⟦br⟧
